 <html:li style="list-style-type: &quot;(i) &quot;">
        A mixed Hodge structure <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[H]]></fr:tex> is <fr:em>torsion free</fr:em> if <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[H_\mathbb {Z}]]></fr:tex> is torsion free.
      </html:li>


      
 <html:li style="list-style-type: &quot;(ii) &quot;">
        If <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[H]]></fr:tex> is torsion free, then we again denote by <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[W]]></fr:tex> the filtration of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[H_\mathbb {Z}\subset \operatorname {H}_\mathbb {Q}]]></fr:tex> induced by <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[W]]></fr:tex>.
